column5: I have been catching a few black crappie while jigging for walleye on LOW. At least that's what I think they are! I have never caught these other years. Are others catching them too?
We catch crappie all the time here (Obabikon Bay on Lake of the Woods). They are deep right now... but we're catching lots of them! (delicious)
Yes, we caught some the same way in June, some were big!
